#: ../../source/unit/imu.rst:2 5bce5943d2a74cadb6b8f7b9228a5fb2
msgid "IMU Unit"
msgstr "IMU Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/imu.rst:6 3eeee44093f14918969f1766a31c0e74
msgid ""
"6-Axis IMU Unit is a 6-axis attitude sensor with 3-axis gravity "
"accelerometer and 3-axis gyroscope, which can calculate tilt angle and "
"acceleration in real time. The chip adopts mpu6886"
msgstr ""
"6-Axis IMU Unit 是一款 6 轴姿态传感器，内置 3 轴重力加速度计和 3 轴陀螺仪，可实时计算倾角和加速度。芯片采用 "
"mpu6886。"

